message.content: The likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are "cs.CL", "cs.IR", "cs.AI", "cs.LG", and "cs.DL". The paper discusses the development of a question answering system for IT support and maintenance domain, which involves natural language understanding, context disambiguation, and deep learning techniques. These topics are closely related to the fields of computational linguistics (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and deep learning (cs.DL).
